public class ClaimAssociationSearchCriteria
extends com.guidewire.pl.persistence.code.BeanBase
implements Versionable, java.io.Serializable
    ClaimAssociationSearchCriteria Non-persistent set of criteria to use in searching for a specific ClaimAssociation. Several of the properties on this entity correspond to properties on the Claims included in the ClaimAssociations, rather than properties of the ClaimAssociations themselves.

    Note that the search controlled by this search criteria entity cannot be customized through the search-config.xml mechanism, and that therefore extensions to this entity will have no effect on the performed search.
